00:24:28.279 --> 00:24:32.279
And in Smallville tonight, police are seeking 17-year-old Sean Kelvin.

00:24:32.639 --> 00:24:36.240
After the mysterious death of fellow Smallville high student Jenna Barnum,

00:24:36.519 --> 00:24:38.399
